    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Kristóf Batthyány (Vienna, 29 November
                    1544)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">Having understood from his letter what benevolence he
                            has in terms of the administration of Oláh’s tithe, he has instructed
                            Tompa to send a reliable person to Batthyány to take the tithe from him.
                            Batthyány should kindly hand over both last year’s tithe as well as this
                            year’s, if possible. What Batthyány has asked him, representing his
                            interests with the King, he has not been able to do yet, but he will get
                            on it now.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Magnifice Domine, Amice Observandissime, salutem! </p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Accepta ex litteris<note type="critic" xml:id="note.1">We do not
                        know this letter.</note> propensa voluntate Magnificae Dominationis Vestrae
                    administrandarum decimarum nostrarum commisimus e vestigio aliis litteris
                    nostris magistro <persName>Georgio Thompa</persName><note type="critic"
                        xml:id="note.2">György Tompa.</note> administratori bonorum episcopatus
                    nostri, ne quam tarditatem in earum negotio admittat, sed statim mittat ad
                    Magnificam Dominationem Vestram certum suum hominem, qui huiusmodi decimas a
                    Magnifica Dominatione Vestra oblatas excipiat. Rogamus itaque eandem, velit
                    gratia mutuae amicitiae tam praeteriti, quam etiam praesentis annorum decimas,
                    (prout se facturum obtulit) reddere.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Quod autem petit nos Magnifica Dominatio Vestra, ut in negotio suo
                    apud regiam maiestatem bonum <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">amicum et</add>
                    patronum ageremus, nostra hactenus in rebus eiusdem intercessio non defuit,
                    neque de cetero erit defutura. Valeat eadem feliciter.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4">Datum <placeName>Viennae</placeName> 29. mensis Novembris
                    MDXLIIII.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.5">
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Nicolaus Olahus episcopus Zagrabiensis
                            etc. manu propria</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.6">Magnifico domino Christophoro de Batthyan pincernarum regalium
                    magistro etc. domino et amico observandissimo.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
